"The user first examines purchasing trends and customer segmentation in the Overview (View 1), selects a time window to analyze category co-occurrence patterns in the Exploration heatmap (View 2), then drills down to specific product combinations in the Detail view (View 4). Simultaneously, payment method preferences are explored through stacked bars (View 3), leading to outlier detection in customer spending patterns at the Insight level (View 5). Selection in any view filters subsequent visualizations through parameter propagation."